ansiCLIrenderer.title: ANSI CLI Image/Video renderer
ansiCLIrenderer.description:
I'm pretty proud of this. Uses ANSI color codes & Unicode lower half block character.
The top "pixel" is the background color, and the bottom is the foreground.
ansiCLIrenderer.summary: Renders images and video in a terminal.
